      ['  5. Amounts must be plain numbers — no currency symbols or commas  (e.g. 45000).'],
      ['  6. Columns marked with * are required — leave optional columns blank if unknown.'],
      ['  7. Dropdown columns (e.g. Status, Condition) have a built-in selector — use it.'],
      ['  8. Save and upload this file in ShopTrack → Settings → Import Data.'],
      [''],
      ['  DATA SHEETS INCLUDED'],
      ['  ├─ Business Info   Your business name, contacts, address and social handles.'],
      ['  ├─ Inventory       Products and items you sell or rent, with prices and stock.'],
      ['  ├─ Customers       Your customer list with contact details and VIP status.'],
      ['  ├─ Vendors         Your suppliers and their contact information.'],
      ['  ├─ Purchases      Supplier purchase orders with costs, freight and duties.'],
      ['  ├─ Sales           Past sales transactions (optional — enter manually too).'],
